LaTeX writer: fix styling if footnote ends with an admonition.

Footnotes in LaTeX are not designed for block-level content and have
therefore uneven spacing around lists, tables, etc.
To work around an overlap with a subsequent footnote, add a `\smallskip`
if a footnote ends with an admonition.

